OL,3,CX Factor finalist makes heart sign
OL,4,Cduring attempted murder court
OL,5,Cappearance
OL,7,FA former X Factor finalist accused of
OL,8,Fattempting to murder a social media
OL,9,Finfluencer by hitting her with a car
OL,10,Fhas appeared in court.
OL,12,FGabriella Carrington allegedly tried
OL,13,Fto kill Klaudia Zakrewska with her
OL,14,FMercedes outside the Inca nightclub on
OL,15,FArgyll Street in Soho, London, at
OL,16,F4.30am on Sunday 19 April 2026.
OL,18,FThe 29-year-old from Manchester made a
OL,19,Fheart sign to her family as she was
OL,20,Fremanded into custody at Westminster
OL,21,FMagistrates' Court on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
