CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776845134
OL,3,CX Factor finalist makes heart sign
OL,4,Cduring attempted murder court
OL,5,Cappearance
OL,7,FMs Zakrzewska, who is in her 30s, is a
OL,8,FTikTok and Instagram influencer who
OL,9,Fgoes by the name Klaudiaglam.
OL,11,FDistrict Judge Nina Tempia ordered
OL,12,Fthat Carrington is held in prison
OL,13,Funtil the next court hearing at the
OL,14,FOld Bailey on 19 May 2026.
OL,16,FOutlining the allegations, prosecutor
OL,17,FRizwan Amin told the court: "In the
OL,18,Fearly hours of Sunday morning, April
OL,19,F19, ambulance services and police were
OL,20,Fcalled to Argyll Street for reports
OL,21,Fthat a woman had been run over.
OL,26,@yD@]OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
