OL,3,CX Factor finalist makes heart sign
OL,4,Cduring attempted murder court
OL,5,Cappearance
OL,7,F"Officers had attended at 5am, and
OL,8,Falso London Ambulance Service were on
OL,9,Fthe scene.
OL,11,F"The scene can only be described as
OL,12,Flots of people shouting, it could be
OL,13,Fdescribed as a melee, so to speak.
OL,15,F"Many individuals who were there were
OL,16,Ffrom a nearby nightclub including
OL,17,Fsecurity staff members.
OL,19,F"The full extent of the incident
OL,20,Fwasn't appreciated at the time
OL,21,Fofficers had attended."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU{D@AOU}D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
