CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776845134
OL,3,CX Factor finalist makes heart sign
OL,4,Cduring attempted murder court
OL,5,Cappearance
OL,7,FThe incident happened on the Soho
OL,8,Fstreet which is home to the London
OL,9,FPalladium theatre.
OL,11,FCarrington, of Broadfield Road,
OL,12,FManchester, has been charged with
OL,13,Fattempted murder, causing grievous
OL,14,Fbodily harm with intent, assault
OL,15,Foccasioning actual bodily harm,
OL,16,Fdangerous driving and drink driving.
OL,18,FShe did not enter any pleas during
OL,19,FTuesday's court hearing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
