OL,3,CX Factor finalist makes heart sign
OL,4,Cduring attempted murder court
OL,5,Cappearance
OL,7,FMs Zakrzewska remains in a life-
OL,8,Fthreatening condition in hospital, the
OL,9,FMetropolitan Police said on Monday
OL,10,Fevening.
OL,12,FThe force said Mr Chyche, in his 50s,
OL,13,Fhas suffered "life-changing injuries".
OL,15,FAfter the charges were announced,
OL,16,FDavid Malone, deputy chief crown
OL,17,Fprosecutor for the CPS in London
OL,18,FNorth, said: "We remind all concerned
OL,19,Fthat proceedings against the defendant
OL,20,Fare active and that she has the right
OL,21,Fto a fair trial.
OL,26,@uD@NOUuD@eO]zD@NOU
